tasks.prompt:
Realistic Style: - [0-3.3 s]: A solid, gray smooth stone sits on a mossy riverbank, beginning to ripple like water across its surface.
- [3.3-6.6 s]: The stone stretches into a soft, organic shape as shimmering metallic wings burst from its sides.
- [6.6-10 s]: The transformed stone flaps its heavy mercury wings and ascends into the air, leaving a trail of floating liquid droplets.

Realistic Style: - [0-3.3 s]: A stack of pancakes on a ceramic plate begins to rhythmically pulse and flatten at the edges.
- [3.3-6.6 s]: The individual pancakes sprout fins and take flight, flapping through a room where gravity has inverted.
- [6.6-10 s]: The pancake-rays migrate into a cloud of steam, turning into translucent amber bubbles that pop into butter droplets.

Realistic Style: - [0-3.3 s]: The roll of Scotch tape begins to violently unspool upward, the adhesive film shimmering in the light.
- [3.3-6.6 s]: The floating tape strips weave and fuse together, sculpting the body and feathers of a transparent sparrow.
- [6.6-10 s]: The tape bird chirps and takes flight, leaving the empty plastic core spinning on the table.

Realistic Style: - [0-3.3 s]: A glowing neon yo-yo spins at the end of a string, beginning to pulse with an inner rhythmic light.
- [3.3-6.6 s]: The yo-yo string thickens into a golden DNA strand as the yo-yo body liquefies and passes through a brick wall.
- [6.6-10 s]: The yo-yo discs explode into hundreds of shimmering digital butterflies that dissipate into a cloud of stardust.
